WELL HOWDY! To all my friends out there that i havnt seen or heard from in AGES! before we start i just want to say that i miss a whole lot of you. I have been extreamly busy. which is an awesome chnage for me. (instead of being stuck at home with nothing to do and stuff) I've been working hard. Ive got a new job at a company called UCMS they do phone stuff for Telstra. Its slightl better than my last job. in where the building is better, the view of southbank is AWESOME! much beter than staring at a wall. hehe. Ive been DJ'in more and more. Aside form runing my night.. which is well slowly picking up, it IS a hard job. The flyers are and have been done they look SHIT HOT! We have a great bunch of DJ's playing. Its just the advertising side of things is a bit of a slut, Ive got 2 people who can start promoting for us. professional promoters who i hope will do a good job. Both female, as you know... male promoters are all about sex drugs and rock n roll. which is GREAT, but not good if you want shit done. i know im male and i LOVE my party. i love it so much not to give a shit on how its run to get people there :P *giggle* Ive also been playing gigs at this lil sunday recovery in the city at this place called WORD. tis just down the lane from the old psyconaut, cute lil place with a great summer coutyard, tis funny its managed by a girl who i met when i was 20, SPIN OUT?! YOU BET Also going to play a gig at billboards in the city... that right my old haunt on a thursday night when Terriyaki was in full swing. now its been cheesed up, not the most ultimate gig.. but for now a gig is a gig, and if im not being asked to perform oral favor im happy :P Because unlike regugitator, im NOT going to suck alot of dick to get where i wanna be. hehe though working for telstra is sucking enough dick :p hehe Ive also started seeing this girl called Claire, which is putting a dumb look on my face most of the day. She is an awesome chick who is quiet intelligent. Which is a strong point due to the fact she is 18. thats right, i AM the hand that is rocking the cradle :P Though she is HAWT! so thats ok a kiss for all you haters Haha! does that mean i can use the phrase, i keep older but they stay the same age. hehe, im lame. But is is away in Byron Bar at the moment...cant wait for her to get back. I met her on my birthday weekend. So, yes. i had an awesome weekend to say the least. So thats been the life of luke. needless to say its been pretty good... rushed as hell. havne'nt had too much time to scratch my nuts. but that might be good thing :P why am i talking about my nuts? probably cause im at work and want something extra to do. we, all should do something soon.... there as been a big hole where you lot once were. how has everyone been, hit me up for a hello and a smile ---over n out----

You see everything though a window. 
You slightly open the door. 
you feel the sun warm the tip of your nose 
you feel the cool breeze across your cheek 
you smell lifes enticing scent 
You want more, you want it all 
You fling the door open and run outside 
letting all of whats beyond your unlocked 
unopened door fill every gap around you 
and with in you.... its beautiful 
Though it will eventally get dark 
And you will eventually have to come inside. 
And all you want to do is to stay outside. 
In the sun, being touched by the breeze, 
being tempted my its aroma. 
But its not ment to last. 
You have to wait for tommorow. 
But the door stays open. It can never be shut 
And staring out at the night 
listening to the promises the stars make 
it will be day again soon 
Where out the windows 
and though the door 
to the other side 
is her.
